    </div>	

	<div class="cleaner">&nbsp;</div>
  	<hr class="noscreen" />    

    <div id="paticka">
     <p class="paticka">Webmaster: Bc. Tomáš Kohout@2013, Technologie: Ruby on Rails</p>
